description.plain: Born as Timothy Cornell Patterson and raised in Sacramento’s Oak Park neighborhood, Mozzy (formerly Lil' Tim) started his career in music at the age of 11, and has hit the ground running, working with notable artists such as Philthy Rich, YG, Red Dot, Stevie Joe, Gunplay, Joe Blow and many more.

songs.title: Sleep Walkin

description.plain: Oak Park California’s own Mozzy gives you a chance to see into the struggles that he faces. “Sleep Walking” is a story of Mozzy’s fight for survival against a looming Judicial System and an ode to all of those who inspire him to prosper
